# Google Fonts Developer API key (free, 10k requests/day).
#
# Only used by the offline build scripts (`npm run catalog:refresh` and
# `npm run pairings:build`) to regenerate the committed data files. The app
# itself reads those static files and needs NO key at runtime — nothing here is
# required to run or host the app.
#
# Enable the "Web Fonts Developer API" in a Google Cloud project, then create an
# API key: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
GOOGLE_FONTS_API_KEY=AIza...
